
Crypto Portfolio Tracker — Flask + CoinGecko API  
A powerful full-stack cryptocurrency portfolio manager built using Flask, SQL, Matplotlib, and the CoinGecko API.  
This project lets users track real-time crypto prices, manage their portfolio, view charts, track their coind, check wallet balance, and more.

Features

Authentication (Flask-Login)
- User Registration  
- Login / Logout  
- Secure session handling  

Portfolio Manager
- Add crypto with buy price & quantity  
- Automatic INR price fetch  
- Live Profit / Loss & P/L %  
- Edit or delete portfolio entries  
- Bar charts & pie charts for portfolio visualization  
Real World Assets Manager
-Add real-world assets with name, CoinGecko ID, and quantity
-Fetch live prices in INR from CoinGecko API
-View total value of all assets
-Remove assets with one click
-Handles both CoinGecko name and ID as input

Wallet Tracker
- Add coins to wallet  
- Automatic live INR rates  
- Inline quantity editing  
- Total wallet value calculation  

Dashboard
- Real-time market prices  
- Coin stats  
- Quick navigation to all sections  

Trending Coins
- Fetches top trending coins from CoinGecko  

Recommended Coins
- Ranks top coins by market cap & volume  
- Includes sparkline charts generated via Matplotlib  
- Fetches live market data using the CoinGecko API  

Caesar Cipher Tool
- Encrypt and decrypt messages  
Hashing preview  
